1. adding new modules
   Add an entry to extensions.bzl in the bazel module:
     bazel/thirdparty/modules/perl-modules/0.0.1.cmk.1/src/extensions.bzl
   Include the CPAN URL and sha256 in the _PERL_MODULES dict.
   Then add the module filename to the appropriate list in module_lists.bzl.

2. updating modules
   Update the URL and sha256 for the module in extensions.bzl.
